{"tid":1657218,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"平等機會委員會主席朱敏健：何君堯「食慣洋腸」言論不恰當，但並非平機會可跟進","createTime":"2019-10-16T03:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T04:55:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cf4bd562aef0463e89cb4a93fff1129660788911","tid":1657218,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:46:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486441-20191016.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486441-20191016.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVqHDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=63c32708\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486441-20191016.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a8d605fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486441-20191016.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1486441_1_L_20191016110539.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1486441_1_L_20191016110539.jpg&h=61135fc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯昨日在立法會內會會議上，被指對議員毛孟靜作出不當的言論而被逐離會議廳。平等機會委員會主席朱敏健出席一個電台節目時表示，有關的言論不恰當，但個案並非平機會可以跟進。<br />\n<br />\n朱敏健說，昨日就事件收到約30個查詢，但由於事件不屬於《性別歧視條例》下懷疑性騷擾的個案，而且在立法會會議廳內發生，所以平機會未能跟進。另外，朱敏健說，自6月中起，收到有關300個查詢，大部分與警方執法方式有關，例如警方在搜身時有不合適行為，部分亦與示威者對女警作出的言論有關。<br />\n<br />\n朱敏健說，到今日為止未有收到投訴，查詢只是詢問平機會的看法，平機會回覆時會表示，性騷擾牽涉到當事人的觀感，所以會邀請安排與當事人見面。"},{"pid":"22f84844940701fd3d7275f995c8a7e5f2831631","tid":1657218,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC4rszp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdC4rszp.jpg&h=a54a4986&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3083bf1418403c0b02fdb45a0c5ae509dbb18416","tid":1657218,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"